 class="s">&#39;scrot screen_%H-%M-%S.png -e \&#39;mv $f ~/Images/screen/\&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class="line" id="LC25">&nbsp;</div><div class="line" id="LC26"><span class="c1"># The Color to use for the variables, needs to be global for logos.pl</span></div><div class="line" id="LC27"><span class="nv">@colors</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span> <span class="s">&quot;\e[0;39m&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;\e[1;34m&quot;</span> <span class="p">);</span></div><div class="line" id="LC28">&nbsp;</div><div class="line" id="LC29"><span class="c1"># Debugging</span></div><div class="line" id="LC30"><span class="k">my</span> <span class="nv">$debug</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class="line" id="LC31"><span class="c1">## End of configuration</span></div><div class="line" id="LC32">&nbsp;</div><div class="line" id="LC33"><span class="c1">########################</span></div><div class="line" id="LC34"><span class="c1">## Script starts here ##</span></div><div class="line" id="LC35"><span class="c1">########################</span></div><div class="line" id="LC36"><span class="nv">@distros</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">();</span></div><div class="line" id="LC37"><span class="nb">require</span> <span class="s">&#39;logos.pl&#39;</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class="line" id="LC38">&nbsp;</div><div class="line" id="LC39"><span class="k">my</span> <span class="nv">$nocolor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&quot;\e[0m&quot;</span><span class="p">;</span></div><div class="line" id="LC40"><span class="k">my</span> <span class="nv">@info</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">();</span></div><div class="line" id="LC41"><span class="k">my</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$DE</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="nv">$WM</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="nv">$theme</s